# User Stories

## Student User Stories
- As a student, I want to register and log in with my student credentials so that I can access the food ordering system securely.
- As a student, I want to browse all available campus food stalls and their menus so that I can decide what to order.
- As a student, I want to filter menu items by dietary preference (e.g., vegetarian, halal) so that I can find suitable food options quickly.
- As a student, I want to add items to a cart and place an order so that I can purchase food without standing in a queue.
- As a student, I want to pay for my order using my campus card or mobile payment so that the checkout process is fast and convenient.
- As a student, I want to receive a real-time notification when my order is ready for collection so that I do not have to wait at the stall.
- As a student, I want to view my order history so that I can easily reorder my favourite meals.
- As a student, I want to rate and review a vendor after my order so that other students can make informed choices.

## Vendor User Stories
- As a vendor, I want to register my food stall and create a menu so that students can discover and order from me.
- As a vendor, I want to update my menu items and mark items as sold out so that students only order what is available.
- As a vendor, I want to receive and manage incoming orders through a dashboard so that I can prepare food efficiently and reduce errors.
- As a vendor, I want to update the status of an order (In Progress / Ready) so that the student is automatically notified.
- As a vendor, I want to view a daily sales summary so that I can track my revenue and popular items.
